    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately not assessed per MRL 2 scope. Discretization error GCI of 7.3% and NIH prediction error of 11.4% are within acceptance criteria. Relative hemolysis index RH < 1 confirmed for worst-case operating condition. The CFD model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis conditions for the Class II CPB device under the stated COU.",
